import './App.css' import { useState } from 'react' import axios from 'axios' function CreatePost() { const [postData, setPostData] = useState({ pfp: '', username: '', location: '', imageLink: '', description: '' }) const handleFormChange = (e) => { setPostData({[e.target.name]: e.target.value}) } const handleFormSubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); const post = { _id: 10, profilePic: postData.pfp, authorName : postData.username, postImg : postData.imageLink, filler : postData.description, likes: 9, commentAuthors: [""], comments: [""], timestamp: 7 } axios .post('http://localhost:3001/post', post) .then(() => console.log('Post Added')) .catch(err => { console.error(err) }) } return (

) } export default CreatePost
